            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Aug 29 /67 ¶ Dear Hector ¶  ¶ […] ¶  ¶ I am glad that Haast is pleased with his FRS. I was not sorry that he had a check the first year, because the "Lord loveth Everyman that he chasteneth" &amp; while I...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">67.08.29</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">Joseph Hooker to James Hector</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Hector papers, Museum of New Zealand, Wellington.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Aug 29 /67</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Hector</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Not relevant.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am glad that Haast is pleased with his FRS. I was not sorry that he had a check the first year, because the "Lord loveth Everyman that he chasteneth" &amp; while I heartily endorse your generous estimate of Haast &amp; kindly feelings towards him, I fancy I see a tendency to that personal destruction that stinks in the nostrils of pure scientific men &amp; has made poor dear Mueller contemptible.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have ventured to warn Haast against this most corrosive &amp; peace destroying snare, &amp; he takes it in admirable part.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Not relevant.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
